title: What Does An Itchy Foot Mean & She Has A Wedding Problem
description:
Kristin's foot is itching like crazy, and she wanted to know why. But she wasn't looking for a logical reason. She was looking for deeper meanings, and what she discovered is freaking her out! Listen!
and
Her stepdad has always been there, but she knows that if she has him walk her down the aisle on her wedding day her estranged bio dad may never be the same! She needs advice on how to keep her wedding from becoming an MMA fight between the two dads!
